question.title: The application could not be installed. Installation failed due to: 'Error code: 'UNKNOWN', message='Unknown failure: '[CDS]close[0]
question.body:
I'm building an android app with android studio code but i'm using a physical device, when i build and run on older androids like 5.0 i get this error. but it works on new android versions like 14.
